    20→ *   3-5 = "Moderate"
    21→ *   5-7 = "Minor"
    22→ *
    23→ * Grade Labels (Strengths):
    24→ *   8-9   = "Good"
    25→ *   9-9.5 = "Excellent"
    26→ *   9.5-10 = "Ideal"
